---
title: Lemon Pepper Chicken Strips with Couscous & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Zesty! Herby! Creamy! This Mediterranean-inspired meal features lemon, garlic and herbs in an easy marinade
for chicken breast strips, while currants and carrot bring colour and flavour to the fluffy couscous.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
